### 2. Backend Layer (Server)

#### [MODIFY] [session-manager.ts](file:///c:/Users/themi/AgentWorkspace/pi-web-wrapper/apps/server/src/pi/session-manager.ts)
- Create and ensure `/tmp/pi-web-users/{username}/workspace` exists.
- In `getOrCreateSession`, instantiate `createAgentSession` and `DefaultResourceLoader` with `cwd: workspaceDir` instead of `cwd: sessionDir`.
- Keep `sessionManager` pointing to `sessionDir` to isolate chat histories.

#### [MODIFY] [files.ts](file:///c:/Users/themi/AgentWorkspace/pi-web-wrapper/apps/server/src/routes/files.ts)
- Implement `/api/workspace/*` endpoints:
  - `GET /api/workspace/*` -> list directory or get file content (base64 for text/media).
  - `PUT /api/workspace/*` -> create files/folders.
  - `POST /api/workspace/*` -> upload files using form data.
  - `DELETE /api/workspace/*` -> delete files/folders.
  - `PATCH /api/workspace/*` -> rename/move files.
- Add validation to prevent path traversal outside `/tmp/pi-web-users/{username}/workspace`.
- Keep `/api/sessions/:sessionId/files/*` routes for backward-compatibility (fallback to workspace directory if file not found in session folder).

